# MenuOS — Robots & AI crawlers

Domain: `https://menuos.gr`

## Policy

- Public marketing content stays open for Google Search and AI crawlers.
- Do **not** block GPTBot, ChatGPT-User, ClaudeBot, or Google-Extended.
- Do **not** disallow landing pages or marketing content.
- Protect only private / operational surfaces.

## Disallow (private)

`/api/`, `/dashboard/`, `/login`, `/register`, `/m/`, `/s/`, `/supervisor/`, `/bds/`, `/kds/`, `/cold/`, `/dessert/`

## Allow

`/`, `/llms.txt` — plus explicit AI user-agent rules with the same Disallow list.

## Discovery

- `https://menuos.gr/llms.txt` — public brand, services, products, marketing URLs only
- `https://menuos.gr/sitemap.xml` + `sitemap-images.xml` — auto-updated with public content

Source of truth: `apps/web/src/app/robots.ts`
